<TITLE> Caritas allocates Tk 10 crore in Sidr relief </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Nov 21 (bdnews24.com) -- Caritas will provide Tk 10 crore in emergency relief to assist 23,500 families worst affected by cyclone Sidr, the NGO said in a statement Wednesday. The nongovernmental organisation will target the worst cyclone-hit areas, including Patuakhali, Barguna and Bagerhat. The aid organisation will also assist in job creation schemes through projects to repair damaged roads, schools and shelters. bd
